	" ALT="
[image ALT: missingALT. It is zzz, further captioned in the text of this webpage.]
	"></TD></TR>
	<TR><TD>
		<P CLASS="a0 center">
The river Nile, between the mountain ranges mentioned by Herodotus.
		<P CLASS="photocredit">
