	"></TD></TR>
	<TR><TD>
		<P CLASS="a0 justify">
<SPAN CLASS="archaic italic">Bennu</SPAN> birds — blue herons — on a papyrus. These birds may be behind the Greek stories about the legendary phoenix.
		<P CLASS="photocredit">
